ing: 1 bunch celery, cut into 1/2 inch pieces
des: "An easy full-flavored soup filled with meat, beans and plenty of vegetables. It will leave you hungry for more!"
ins:
Place the beef stew meat and onions in a medium saucepan. Cook and stir over medium heat until evenly brown
In a large saucepan, place the meat, onions, tomato juice, celery, green beans, carrots, peas, bay leaves, salt and pepper. Bring to a boil. Reduce heat and simmer 4 hours.
Stir in the kidney beans. Cook 15 minutes longer and serve warm.
